Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发睡得好乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前开始就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部再注意一下头发就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得长得这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 丘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 怎么啦你的头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发睡得很乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么严重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也很像卜部的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子必须注意下头发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 很刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你总是用刘海遮住眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部改变发型露出眼睛的话 形象会改变很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 这么难得 要不今天整天都保持这个发型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露出眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都认不出是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 束起刘海很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我梳的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然头一回看到卜部束起刘海的样子 还挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然至今都认为她是个怪人 但今天的得分很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要不要去追卜部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想去厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也是这个发型去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为弄这个发型的是丘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘明天也弄我的头发的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会变成这个发型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天开始不要弄这个发型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想你变回原来的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问为什么 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔只有我能看到的卜部的素面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让大家看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把双手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双手？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要干啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这双手将我的头发尽情弄乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力点 弄到很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 原来的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿不喜欢那个发型的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看过去 感觉这个发型对我来说才是最可爱的发型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被椿弄乱头发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了跟卜部很相称的新发型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完便当去更衣室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的形象改变 不是得到班里的好评吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是意大利面熏肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以作为主食的新烹调法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也挑战一下新发型好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说免了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 卜部被椿说变回原来的发型了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好像是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为椿独占欲好像很强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独占欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿对因变了发型 而被其它男生看到卜部的素面这事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 心跳得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 昨天被椿说变回原来的发型的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让椿做了很舒服的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的事情…怎样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用双手抓住我的头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥要做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由你就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后能就这样搅乱我的头发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之试试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜起雾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被喜欢的人弄乱头发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人 总是做些奇怪的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一张300円买不买
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前卜部不是换过一天的发型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天我偷拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 竟然做到那个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很罕见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新看一看 卜部果然很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要这张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 300円
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时前发遮着眼睛都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要这张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别推我别推我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这群混蛋公狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身为男朋友的我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买卖连我都很少见到的卜部的素面的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想现在就对这群家伙宣言 卜部是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面目狰狞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一脸着急的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那种表情吗 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为真的很不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部明明是我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只属于我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我的独占欲很强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 上野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为男朋友的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要「大家都有的照片」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实我真的很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有丘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这样看着卜部 是不是有点像今井百夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说起来还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这种有点锐利的眼神非常像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 是不是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确很像今井百夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像卜部的女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 今井百夏是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们同校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 人家是偶像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啦 最近因为饮用水广告红起来的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个广告很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我买了写真集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张照片真的很像今井百夏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然比起百夏 有点冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有个很像卜部的偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么椿 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 平时的话都会这么直接回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天回家之前先去书店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去结账
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了买了 我就买下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想赶紧回去看里面的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这不是椿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见啊 居然会在书店碰见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你买什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏的写真集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为听说是最近成为话题的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉偶尔看看这些流行物也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 真的很像卜部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有泳衣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部是卜部的更大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这也有可爱之处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部就是这种满脸的笑容很少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买了好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在男生之间贩卖着卜部同学的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影部不是有个叫中岛的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙用一张300円的价格在卖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 公平买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没买
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有丘在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那椿呢 椿买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那家伙也没买
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是椿其实很喜欢卜部那种样子的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道那种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在刚才那个书店 那家伙买了今井百夏的写真集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:17:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部同学长得很像今井百夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今井百夏是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在当红的偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像我的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿也买了这个人的写真集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天听上野说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是长得很像卜部同学才买的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得好像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 卜部 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿有今井百夏的写真集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听丘同学说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上野—丘—卜部的路线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就封住上野的口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个偶像很像我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了那个人的写真集是因为她长得很像卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说会喜欢上那个偶像是因为我喜欢卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…怎么说呢 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看那个写真集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那个公园里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把那个写真集拿来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 是吧 长得很像卜部对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己看也这样觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本写真集里椿最喜欢的照片是哪张？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我最喜欢的照片是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 保持这样不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道要发动内裤剪刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿是我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想没必要喜欢上长得像我的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 椿 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不止是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的独占欲也很强？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉发了很大的火啊
